item.title: Custom dragon armor release
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

In my humble honest opinion… this looks strange when worn. I’m not saying It’s bad, but I don’t like it. These are the type of Customs that Veteran Players tend to dislike or avoid. I don’t know why the RuneScape Private Server Community like to have black wings on their Characters. I mean, I can understand Administrators having wings of some sort, but they should be there to help Players be able to instantly differentiate Administrative Staffers from others. Something that stands out and looks good. There are already Flight Animations prepared for Player Characters. Perhaps using this Animation + REAL Custom wings? Here’s an example of the type of wings I had in mind:

2012HugeUprightAngelWingsFront5128dm_small.jpg331×502

P.S. The Model you posted has holes in the wings. I don’t think they would be very aerodynamic.

I’m not criticizing this - just giving my feedback.
